{
  "title": "Plataforma Desafiar — Radar de Saúde",
  "description": "Dashboard executivo para gestores. Mostra uptime do ITOKEN, dispositivos, squads e incidentes. Atualizado automaticamente.",
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "reflow_type": "fixed",
  "tags": ["team:plataforma-desafiar", "env:production", "tipo:executivo"],
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "env",
      "prefix": "env",
      "available_values": ["production", "staging"],
      "default": "production"
    },
    {
      "name": "squad",
      "prefix": "squad",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    }
  ],
  "widgets": [

    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "title": "🔒 Camada Zero — ITOKEN",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "widgets": [

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "service_level_objective",
              "title": "SLO — Disponibilidade ITOKEN",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "view_type": "detail",
              "slo_id": "SUBSTITUA_PELO_ID_DO_SEU_SLO",
              "show_error_budget": true,
              "view_mode": "overall",
              "time_windows": ["7d", "30d", "90d"],
              "global_time_target": "99.9"
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 3 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "timeseries",
              "title": "Latência ITOKEN — p50 / p95 / p99",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1", "alias": "p50" }],
                  "queries": [{
                    "name": "query1",
                    "data_source": "metrics",
                    "query": "p50:trace.itoken.validation.duration{env:$env} by {service}"
                  }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": { "palette": "blue", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "normal" }
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query2", "alias": "p95" }],
                  "queries": [{
                    "name": "query2",
                    "data_source": "metrics",
                    "query": "p95:trace.itoken.validation.duration{env:$env} by {service}"
                  }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": { "palette": "orange", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "normal" }
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query3", "alias": "p99" }],
                  "queries": [{
                    "name": "query3",
                    "data_source": "metrics",
                    "query": "p99:trace.itoken.validation.duration{env:$env} by {service}"
                  }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "style": { "palette": "red", "line_type": "dashed", "line_width": "thin" }
                }
              ],
              "yaxis": { "include_zero": true, "scale": "linear" },
              "markers": [
                { "value": "y = 500", "display_type": "warning dashed", "label": "SLA 500ms" },
                { "value": "y = 1000", "display_type": "error dashed", "label": "Limite crítico 1s" }
              ]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 4, "y": 0, "width": 8, "height": 3 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Taxa de Erro ITOKEN (últimas 24h)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "autoscale": false,
              "precision": 2,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "(errors / total) * 100", "alias": "% erro" }],
                "queries": [
                  { "name": "errors", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:itoken.validation.errors{env:$env}.as_count()", "aggregator": "sum" },
                  { "name": "total", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:itoken.validation.requests{env:$env}.as_count()", "aggregator": "sum" }
                ],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 1, "palette": "white_on_red" },
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 0.1, "palette": "white_on_yellow" },
                  { "comparator": "<=", "value": 0.1, "palette": "white_on_green" }
                ]
              }],
              "suffix": "%"
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Validações ITOKEN (hoje)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:itoken.validation.requests{env:$env}.as_count()",
                  "aggregator": "sum"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar"
              }],
              "timeseries_background": { "type": "bars", "yaxis": { "include_zero": true } }
            },
            "layout": { "x": 2, "y": 3, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "timeseries",
              "title": "Volume de Validações ITOKEN — últimos 30 dias",
              "title_size": "13",
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [
                  { "formula": "success", "alias": "Sucesso" },
                  { "formula": "errors", "alias": "Erros" }
                ],
                "queries": [
                  { "name": "success", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:itoken.validation.success{env:$env}.as_count()" },
                  { "name": "errors", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:itoken.validation.errors{env:$env}.as_count()" }
                ],
                "response_format": "timeseries",
                "display_type": "bars",
                "style": { "palette": "green" }
              }],
              "show_legend": true
            },
            "layout": { "x": 4, "y": 3, "width": 8, "height": 2 }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 12, "height": 1 }
    },

    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "title": "📱 Dispositivos — Validação & Habilitação",
        "background_color": "vivid_purple",
        "widgets": [

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Validados (este mês)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:plataforma.device.validated{env:$env,squad:$squad}.as_count()",
                  "aggregator": "sum"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [{ "comparator": ">", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green" }]
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Habilitados (este mês)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:plataforma.device.enabled{env:$env,squad:$squad}.as_count()",
                  "aggregator": "sum"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [{ "comparator": ">", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green" }]
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 2, "y": 0, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Bloqueados agora",
              "title_size": "13",
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:plataforma.device.blocked{env:$env,squad:$squad}",
                  "aggregator": "last"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 5, "palette": "white_on_red" },
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_yellow" },
                  { "comparator": "<=", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green" }
                ]
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 4, "y": 0, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Tempo Médio Unblocking (p50)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "autoscale": false,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1 / 60000", "alias": "minutos" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "p50:plataforma.device.unblocking_duration_ms{env:$env,squad:$squad}",
                  "aggregator": "avg"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 60, "palette": "white_on_red" },
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_yellow" },
                  { "comparator": "<=", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_green" }
                ]
              }],
              "suffix": " min"
            },
            "layout": { "x": 6, "y": 0, "width": 3, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "change",
              "title": "Variação de Dispositivos vs mês anterior",
              "title_size": "13",
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:plataforma.device.enabled{env:$env,squad:$squad}.as_count()",
                  "aggregator": "sum"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "change_type": "absolute",
                "compare_to": "month_before",
                "increase_good": true,
                "order_by": "change",
                "order_dir": "desc",
                "show_present": true
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 9, "y": 0, "width": 3, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "timeseries",
              "title": "Dispositivos por Status — linha do tempo",
              "title_size": "13",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1", "alias": "Validados" }],
                  "queries": [{ "name": "query1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:plataforma.device.validated{env:$env,squad:$squad}.as_count().rollup(sum, 86400)" }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "bars",
                  "style": { "palette": "purple" }
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query2", "alias": "Habilitados" }],
                  "queries": [{ "name": "query2", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:plataforma.device.enabled{env:$env,squad:$squad}.as_count().rollup(sum, 86400)" }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "bars",
                  "style": { "palette": "green" }
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query3", "alias": "Bloqueados" }],
                  "queries": [{ "name": "query3", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:plataforma.device.blocked{env:$env,squad:$squad}.as_count().rollup(sum, 86400)" }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "bars",
                  "style": { "palette": "red" }
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "width": 12, "height": 3 }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 1, "width": 12, "height": 1 }
    },

    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "title": "🤝 Squads — Suporte & Unblocking",
        "background_color": "vivid_green",
        "widgets": [

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "toplist",
              "title": "Squads com mais solicitações (este mês)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1", "alias": "Solicitações", "limit": { "count": 10, "order": "desc" } }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:plataforma.squad.requests{env:$env}.as_count() by {squad}",
                  "aggregator": "sum"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "style": { "palette": "datadog16" }
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 3 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "toplist",
              "title": "Squads com maior tempo de unblocking (p95)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1 / 60000", "alias": "minutos (p95)", "limit": { "count": 10, "order": "desc" } }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "p95:plataforma.device.unblocking_duration_ms{env:$env} by {squad}",
                  "aggregator": "percentile"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 60, "palette": "white_on_red" },
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_yellow" },
                  { "comparator": "<=", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_green" }
                ]
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 4, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 3 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "timeseries",
              "title": "Tempo médio de unblocking por squad — tendência",
              "title_size": "13",
              "show_legend": true,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1 / 60000", "alias": "minutos" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "p50:plataforma.device.unblocking_duration_ms{env:$env,squad:$squad} by {squad}"
                }],
                "response_format": "timeseries",
                "style": { "palette": "datadog16", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "normal" }
              }],
              "markers": [
                { "value": "y = 30", "display_type": "ok dashed", "label": "Meta 30min" },
                { "value": "y = 60", "display_type": "error dashed", "label": "Limite 60min" }
              ]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 8, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 3 }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "width": 12, "height": 1 }
    },

    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "title": "🛡️ Incidentes & Confiabilidade",
        "background_color": "vivid_orange",
        "widgets": [

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "alert_graph",
              "title": "Status dos Monitors Críticos agora",
              "title_size": "13",
              "alert_id": "SUBSTITUA_PELO_ID_DO_MONITOR_ITOKEN",
              "viz_type": "timeseries"
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 3 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "event_timeline",
              "title": "Timeline de Eventos — Incidentes e Deploys",
              "title_size": "13",
              "query": "tags:team:plataforma-desafiar",
              "tags_execution": "and"
            },
            "layout": { "x": 4, "y": 0, "width": 8, "height": 3 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "Monitors em ALERT agora",
              "title_size": "13",
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "sum:datadog.monitor.triggered{team:plataforma-desafiar,status:alert}",
                  "aggregator": "last"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 2, "palette": "white_on_red" },
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_yellow" },
                  { "comparator": "<=", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green" }
                ]
              }]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "query_value",
              "title": "MTTR médio (últimos 30 dias)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "autoscale": false,
              "precision": 0,
              "requests": [{
                "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1 / 60", "alias": "minutos" }],
                "queries": [{
                  "name": "query1",
                  "data_source": "metrics",
                  "query": "avg:plataforma.incident.resolution_time_seconds{env:$env}",
                  "aggregator": "avg"
                }],
                "response_format": "scalar",
                "conditional_formats": [
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 60, "palette": "white_on_red" },
                  { "comparator": ">", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_yellow" },
                  { "comparator": "<=", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_green" }
                ]
              }],
              "suffix": " min"
            },
            "layout": { "x": 2, "y": 3, "width": 2, "height": 2 }
          },

          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "timeseries",
              "title": "Incidentes P1/P2 por semana — últimos 90 dias",
              "title_size": "13",
              "show_legend": true,
              "requests": [
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query1", "alias": "P1 — Crítico" }],
                  "queries": [{ "name": "query1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:plataforma.incident.count{env:$env,severity:p1}.as_count().rollup(sum, 604800)" }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "bars",
                  "style": { "palette": "red" }
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query2", "alias": "P2 — Alto" }],
                  "queries": [{ "name": "query2", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:plataforma.incident.count{env:$env,severity:p2}.as_count().rollup(sum, 604800)" }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "bars",
                  "style": { "palette": "orange" }
                },
                {
                  "formulas": [{ "formula": "query3", "alias": "Interceptados (evitados)" }],
                  "queries": [{ "name": "query3", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "sum:plataforma.incident.intercepted{env:$env}.as_count().rollup(sum, 604800)" }],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "line",
                  "style": { "palette": "green", "line_type": "dashed" }
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": { "x": 4, "y": 3, "width": 8, "height": 2 }
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "width": 12, "height": 1 }
    },

    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "## 📌 Como usar este dashboard\n\n**Para gestores:** use o seletor de período no topo (últimos 30 dias = visão mensal). Os widgets em **vermelho** precisam de atenção imediata.\n\n**Para Tech Leads:** filtre por `squad` para ver o impacto por time. O grupo *Squads* mostra quem mais demanda e onde o unblocking está lento.\n\n**Métricas customizadas necessárias:**\n- `plataforma.device.validated` — evento de dispositivo validado\n- `plataforma.device.enabled` — evento de dispositivo habilitado\n- `plataforma.device.blocked` — gauge de dispositivos bloqueados\n- `plataforma.device.unblocking_duration_ms` — histograma do ciclo\n- `plataforma.squad.requests` — contador de solicitações por squad\n- `plataforma.incident.intercepted` — contador de incidentes evitados\n- `plataforma.incident.resolution_time_seconds` — histograma de MTTR\n\n**SLO e Monitor IDs:** substitua `SUBSTITUA_PELO_ID_DO_SEU_SLO` e `SUBSTITUA_PELO_ID_DO_MONITOR_ITOKEN` pelos IDs reais do seu ambiente.",
        "background_color": "gray",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "top",
        "show_tick": false,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "left",
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": { "x": 0, "y": 99, "width": 12, "height": 6 }
    }
  ]
}